" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90229042dfd313586d3cb59896e9580147455302","tid":1334403,"uid":267493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:54:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76face69798f0249bebf16ddb89ab8629d7a1adf","tid":1334403,"uid":63093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c977a43d95010bfe3385ad84f4e0c0f23562d6a3","tid":1334403,"uid":276469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15a11200dcecd3b1b11a843f4b7bf2883d4f7b6","tid":1334403,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即刻follow 我地個telegram channel先啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HongKong_Scout_Info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHongKong_Scout_Info&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvboeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=9b9fcc2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HongKong_Scout_Info</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好！距離721只有一日時間<br />\n呢個po既班底係分別來自：<br />\n【7.21 HongKongner Online】全民支援  第四代即時通訊系統：戰略互動地圖 急需開發人員/測試人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328555\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328555</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n同<br />\n<br />\n721 情報站成形準備工作!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325999\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n基本上係base on情報站post 組左隊開始研究 跟著再同開發人員既it人合作<br />\n<br />\n因為有鑑於往往發夢時 無論發夢企前線定處於後方既人好多時候未必掌握到即時現場環境既情況/事態發展<br />\n同時因為有大量情報湧現 （無論係現場哨兵回報 網上live 或者係連登）會導致消息混亂既情況。再者，呢d情報大多數可能係未經fact check就隨意發放會令前線不能作出一個有效既計劃。<br />\n<br />\n所以 我地就決定要嘗試將以上既野盡量解決！<br />\n同時出呢個post既原因除左比各位知道有呢一個平台之外 仲想帶出其實<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">情報有效傳達既重要性</span></strong>係同first aid, 物資<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>對等</strong></span>！！<br />\n<br />\n經過幾日既討論，大致上都已經有左個雛形。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">宗旨</span></strong></span><br />\n只發放消息（任何消息都一定經我方哨兵fact check）<br />\n不分析<br />\n不指揮<br />\n『係一個純粹發放凖確消息比前線同後方既一個平台』<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的</span></strong></span><br />\n- 發放對家佈防資訊<br />\n- 發放我方前線位置<br />\n（因為成個平台都只係係雛形，所以物資情報站暫時唔做）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">消息發佈平台</span></span></strong><br />\n<ins>1. Telegram Channel</ins><br />\n- 公佈現場資訊板位置<br />\n- 公佈公用電台頻道<br />\n- 發佈與現場資訊板大致相同內容<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2. 現場公眾資訊板</ins><br />\n- 資訊板由白板memo同彩色磁石組成，不斷由我方發佈員更新，資訊會連timestamp確保up to date<br />\n- 資訊板位置會在telegram channel 公佈<br />\n<br />\n<ins>3. 前線通訊兵</ins><br />\n- 由我方平台招攬嘅通訊兵向前線發放最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<ins>4. 現場實時地圖</ins><br />\n- web based app形式<br />\n- 用地圖及不同類型既icon以圖像化方式可以知道不同方位前線既最新消息<br />\n<br />\n<ins>5. 公用電台頻道</ins><br />\n- 礙於頻道任何人都可以發言，所以只會發佈簡單但重要資訊<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">人才招募</span></span></strong><br />\n我地仍然需要大量人力幫我地收集、整理資訊。特別適合和理非或者有包袱人士。<br />\n如果你成日去夢遊都唔知做緊乜，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">加入我地啦！</span></span></strong><br />\n如果你嫌熱唔想出嚟，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">加入我地啦！</span></span></strong><br />\n如果你驚落雨濕身，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加入我地啦！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n時日無多，即刻電郵聯絡我地啦！<br />\n[url]semperoccultus0@protonmail.ch[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>最後再講多次</strong></span></span><br />\n即刻follow我地個telegram channel，確保收到最新消息！<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HongKong_Scout_Info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHongKong_Scout_Info&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvboeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=9b9fcc2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HongKong_Scout_Info</a><br />\n<br />\n721見！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:03:42.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"67b20e102ee139c8ea648340b5ae36af9bac2abb","tid":1334403,"uid":180657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:45:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1caf7643042ff27e2e3cd8d13411ba735e2c3f5","tid":1334403,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b9bf91661e118306da5239016525132fec542bd","tid":1334403,"uid":280264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"8cb4f68a0d3f1f5cdd1d2576c13f87dc21f85de2","tid":1334403,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:08:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fec82dd2c3656d493953decb29e617a66450a4c4","tid":1334403,"uid":260848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1a4423fc27ebd99b134863ad65791fe57161558","tid":1334403,"uid":137009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bc088b8a35ca31efeee078ad891f8c9acd35069","tid":1334403,"uid":187935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:38:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"744e388c5718bbca791f92e37413149536c8b55b","tid":1334403,"uid":279567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e640465b98f8f7f2dd359a8dbb508d97e444561","tid":1334403,"uid":122185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"即刻去買"},{"pid":"caf348b3001c449b7b140079d709f785ec8dec49","tid":1334403,"uid":114416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2943965d1a7cc054dce596d3292f42cfb865421a","tid":1334403,"uid":85082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class